1 shal l investigate any possible criminal violation of the law related
2 to the absentee ballot requests.
3 3. Provided, this notification requirement shall not apply to
4 requests for absentee ballots to be sent to the addresses of nursing
5 homes, veterans centers, medical facilities, multiunit housing,
6 installations of the Armed Forces of the United States where
7 uniformed or overseas voters, as defined by the Uniformed and
8 Overseas Citizens Absentee Voting Act, are stationed or other
9 locations authorized in writing by the Secretary of the State
10 Election Board.
11 E. The provisions of this section shall only apply to an
12 election conducted by a county election board, the State Election
13 Board or a political subdivision of this state.
14 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
